
Nine Men's Morris 3D

======================================================================

OVERVIEW

	Nine Men's Morris 3D is an adaption of the popular correspondent board game. 
	The game is visualized in 3D and programmed for web browsers. You can play 
	against a computer opponent or another human.

	Features:
	- 3D visualization with three.js
	- implemented rule check
	- AI with Alpha Beta Pruning
	- advanced AI Estimator
	- use of genetic algorithms to improve the Estimator

